 style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞</span>"},{"pid":"2c04b1e7031a26ce77ec1828a7a2ba6f031ba232","tid":1786721,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"無人想知呀"},{"pid":"e26e2f6be8c97ca7415326ed95451c19da4625a6","tid":1786721,"uid":171668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"成日講佢把撚呀！？<br />\n無人識佢呀<br />\n點解要成日講個無關痛癢既人？"},{"pid":"5c95d907b4c4ea73fe88bc72a0e5a258e42e779b","tid":1786721,"uid":40684,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"這個男孩子全部財產是4萬港幣，過着流浪漢的生活，他們只會跟我說：不要胡鬧<br />\n港男成副身家得4萬港幣, 她會跟我說：不要胡鬧"},{"pid":"901f5b94091be9d27037bfada818092721220d7b","tid":1786721,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"未來能否成為真正的伴侶？我們都不能確定；<br />\n姐係俾人屌完就走 當人地條女<br />\n佢知唔知人哋日日都係咁樣呃女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d75e22f9a47ddddb1fde4ed7875cde8dc2ebd92","tid":1786721,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"邊撚陳慧敏屌你老母咁都有新聞"},{"pid":"a0c2130791b489481a57abeaddfb1ed8b19c51c8","tid":1786721,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"見到堆千字文就唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />煩西到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd62449250bf1462d8f49e997aec17da1df0dfc","tid":1786721,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:05:46.000Z","msg":"當中喺埃及更慘遭非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}